document.full_text: the israeli military was searching on saturday for a palestinian intruder, or intruders, it accused of stabbing to death five members of an israeli family in the west bank settlement of itamar friday night.
document.title: suspecting palestinians, israeli military hunts for killers of 5 west bank settlers
